desktop_statistics_tip:
Total desktops: The total number of classrooms introduced by the service management portal (VDI, VOI, IDV) + introduced service desktops + personal desktops (VDI personal desktops + personal desktop pool + roaming desktops);
Online desktops: The number of connected classroom desktops + connected service desktops + connected personal desktops;
Offline desktops: Total desktops - online desktops;

